<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạsmʿhạ yạ kẖạṭy klmẗ .. bạqwlhạ wbạ̹ṣrạr
 mạfysẖ lḥyạtk mʿny̱ .. mn gẖyr yswʿ ạlbạr)2
 ạlqrạr- (mạ tslm qlbk lyh .. wḥmwlk ạ̹rmy ʿlyh
 hạykẖly ḥyạtk gẖnwẗ .. mlyạnẗ bạltsbyḥ
 hạtʿysẖ ḥyạẗ ạlnwr .. ṭwl ạ̉yạmk msrwr
 wlạ hm ykẖbṭ ʿly̱ bạbk .. dmh ysẖfy ạlkswr)2
 2- (lyh ʿạysẖ bạnksạr .. qlbk dạymaⁿạ mḥtạr
 mtqlb fy ạlạ̉fkạr .. msẖ lạqy lnfsk dạr)2
 3- (hạtʿysẖ mhmạ tʿysẖ .. ạlʿmr dạ msẖ hạyzyd
 ywm ḥzn wywm tgẖryd .. wʿnạdk msẖ hạyfyd)2</lyrics>
<title>ạsmʿhạ yạ kẖạṭy klmẗ</title>
</song>